OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another dry day with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine though a bit more
OL,7,Fcloud than previous days. Warm again
OL,8,Fin the west, but a bit cooler around
OL,9,FGreater Glasgow.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with plenty of
OL,12,Fsunshine to enjoy. Cloud filling in
OL,13,Fduring the night with some light rain
OL,14,Faround the islands by dawn.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSunday:FCloudy with some light rain
OL,17,Ffor Argyll, some brighter spells
OL,18,Fdeveloping later in the day, winds
OL,19,Fremaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
